Liverpool will travel to Manchester City on Tuesday taking nothing for granted but determined to seal a place in the Champions League semi-finals, insists Sadio Man&eacute;, writes @__ChrisShaw<br />
<br />
Man&eacute;: &ldquo;Of course we have a chance. It will not be easy for both teams but we&rsquo;re going to go there and try to do our best and qualify &ndash; for the club and for the fans.&rdquo;

J&uuml;rgen Klopp's instructions to Dominic Solanke before he entered the maelstrom that was Liverpool versus Manchester City were simple, writes @SamWiIliams<br />
<br />
Solanke: &ldquo;Make sure that we keep the pressure on, don&rsquo;t let them get too much of an advantage. We knew that we were a big scoreline up so we wanted to keep that for the second leg. We managed to keep a clean sheet so it worked.&rdquo;

